item.title: Help with starting my server for people!
item.dc:creator: @Ncarug01 Ncarug01
item.description:
@Ncarug01 wrote:

i used to have the same problem myself make sure you’ve port forwarded on your router correctly
make sure you’ve opened port 43594 on your firewall
make sure your start and end port forwarding on your router is start 43594 end 43594
and make sure if you have a linksys router make sure your end address is 3 digits not 2 or 1
to find your ip address go to start>run>cmd then type in ipconfig and youll see your ending ip address here
shown here
